OL,5, A prototype "lickable" TV screen which 
OL,6, can mimic food flavours has been       
OL,7, developed by a Japanese professor,     
OL,8, Reuters reports.                       
OL,10,FDubbed Taste-the-TV, ten canisters     
OL,11,Fspray flavour onto a "hygienic film"   
OL,12,Fwhich is rolled over the screen for the
OL,13,Fviewer to lick.                        
OL,15,FProfessor Homei Miyashita of Meiji     
OL,16,FUniversity, suggested it could be used 
OL,17,Fto train cooks or sommeliers remotely, 
OL,19,FIf made commercially, the TV would cost
OL,20,F$875 (#735), he estimated.             
